qayamat se qayamat tak ( from doom till doom ) , also known by the initialism qsqt , is a 1988 indian hindi-language romantic drama film directed by mansoor khan . written and produced by nasir hussain , the film is an adaptation of romeo and juliet by william shakespeare . it stars aamir khan and juhi chawla in the lead roles . the film was released on 29 april 1988 to critical acclaim , and was a major success , turning khan and chawla into hugely popular stars . composed by anand-milind , the soundtrack of the film was equally successful and popular . indiatimes movies ranks the movie amongst the " top 25 must see bollywood films " . it won the national film award for best popular film providing wholesome entertainment , and eight filmfare awards from eleven nominations including best film , and best director for mansoor khan .